 1.186  : (29.10.95)
        + First release version.

 1.187  : (29.10.95)
        + Added informaton about Umentiler being pure to the docs.

 1.188  : (13.11.95)
        + Added NOPARSEDATE option to the Version command.

 1.208  : (10.01.96)
        + Added the TAG command.
        + Added calls to SetVBuf() in order to improve performance with WB 3.1.
        + Added BUFFER option to main program.
          (Thanks to Magnus Holmgren for the suggestions)

 1.211  : (28.01.96)
        + Documented the BUFFER program argument which was added in the last
          release
        + Reduced default BUFFER size from 16k to 4k.
        + Added DOLLERCUT option to the TAG command.
        + Added USETAG option to the VERSION command.
          (Hopefully Magnus will be happy ;)
